description.value:
Override of MedicationCode to support existing implementations using dm+d SNOMED CT. A set of codes from the following dm+d (dictionary of medicines and devices) concept classes that define a medication: 
 - VTM – Virtual Therapeutic Moiety;
 - VMP – Virtual Medicinal Product;
 - AMP – Actual Medicinal Product;
 - VMPP – Virtual Medicinal Product Pack;
 - AMPP – Actual Medicinal Product Pack

